snippet.title: Let's talk about 1 MILLION PEOPLE wanting to fire Amber Heard
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp's fans are ANGRY at Warner Brothers for firing him from the FANTASTIC BEASTS franchise, so they have taken to Change.org to demand that Amber Heard also be terminated from the AQUAMAN franchise. So far over 1 MILLION PEOPLE are wanting to see Mera replaced with someone like Emilia Clarke (who BossLogic also supports in the role). If Johnny Depp wins his defamation lawsuit against Amber Heard next year, will Warner Bro's follow suit and fire Amber Heard? Let's talk about it.
